metadata.name: Goat #1
metadata.description:
Our vision is to find MOFO (motivated and focused) talent and present them to the world! The GOATS reward creators and fans alike
  GOATS will incentivize innovation and collaboration from great minds everywhere.
  This digital art collection of unique Goat NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain represents the passion, heart, talents, and confidence of the GOAT community.
